{"type":"message","id":"17855eb6","parentId":"5bad6dfb","timestamp":"2026-03-29T09:04:25.733Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-03-29 17:04 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索道简网络相关行业的最新动态，整理3-5条关键信息，保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\n行业关键词：企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务、弱电工程、系统集成商\n\n要求：\n1. 搜索最近3个月内的行业动态和政策\n2. 每条信息包含：标题、来源、摘要（100字内）、对道简网络的参考意义\n3. 使用中文输出\n4. 文件格式为Markdown\n\n输出文件路径：/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n文件开头标注：# 行业动态学习笔记（2026-03-29）"}],"timestamp":1774775065729}}
{"type":"message","id":"ff5ad827","parentId":"17855eb6","timestamp":"2026-03-29T09:04:31.558Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to search for industry news related to 道简网络's business: 企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务、弱电工程、系统集成商. \n\nLet me search for recent (last 3 months) industry dynamics and policies. I'll use the web search skill first.","thinkingSignature":"89b66cb223f2c2f24d7a7c3dbad33b85e98ae3d5499d7da203c507781cb69aea"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_o7hf3qxsw9qr_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":117,"output":100,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":42210,"totalTokens":42427,"cost":{"input":0.0000351,"output":0.00011999999999999999,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0050652,"total":0.0052203}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774775065731}}
{"type":"message","id":"c66a5077","parentId":"ff5ad827","timestamp":"2026-03-29T09:04:31.569Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_o7hf3qxsw9qr_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774775071566}}
{"type":"message","id":"e1aa38c0","parentId":"c66a5077","timestamp":"2026-03-29T09:04:37.547Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll perform multiple searches in parallel to gather information about the industry trends related to 道简网络's business. Let me search for:\n1. 企业数字化转型政策 2026年\n2. 智能安防行业动态 2026\n3. 网络系统集成行业动态 2026\n4. IT运维服务行业动态 2026\n5. 弱电工程行业动态 2026","thinkingSignature":"95b4c04dbbbde191077548b9031b74f1f31ff4cce064d118753ed27741c9375f"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uucr3jm1hrr4_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型政策 2026年 一季度\" 2>/dev/null","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uucr3jm1hrr4_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业动态 2026年\" 2>/dev/null","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_uucr3jm1hrr4_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维服务 弱电工程 行业动态 2026\" 2>/dev/null","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":943,"output":256,"cacheRead":41999,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43198,"cost":{"input":0.0002829,"output":0.0003072,"cacheRead":0.0012599699999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018500699999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774775071568}}
